        public int doEndTag()
        Creates Scripting variables for:
        • SlingHttpServletRequest
        • SlingHttpServletResponse
        • current Resource
        • current Node (if resource is adaptable to a node)
        • current Logger
        • current SlingScriptHelper
        Returns:
